name: CRPTD_Artifacts Mint Pass
description:
1000 Corrupted Artifacts decimated into 1/1's and distributed across Scrambler City.

Hold this token to receive your CRPTD_Artifact before the S0lst1ce.

CRPTD_Artifacts are new, higher-value currency in Scrambler City, and can be traded for contraband.

Holders of CRPTD_Artifacts will also be eligible for a penthouse apartment in Scrambler City, and control of the r00t distribution cartel.

CRPTD_Artifacts are created by @alexdelia (with special guests) for Artifact Quest.
2021.
